{"type":"message","id":"8720e750","parentId":"0e119ad1","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:22:04.099Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:news-monitor-001 盘中舆情监控] 执行新闻监控：1.搜索最新突发财经新闻 2.评估对持仓影响 3.若是Level 3级黑天鹅，自动触发紧急部署 4.仅在有重大风险时通知用户\nCurrent time: Monday, March 9th, 2026 — 5:22 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1773048124098}}
